quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  15,16,"Ni ej galaxies en des cxiel, ornam gxi beholders"
  15,17,Ni gard gxi cxiu rejected diabl
  15,18,any da them sneaks auxskult tre projectile vol pel him dors
  15,19,As por ter ni konstru gxi ej gxi stabilizers (mont) ni kresk gxi perfekt balance de cxio
  15,20,Ni far gxi habitable vi kaj creatures vi ne do proviz por
  15,21,tie est nothing ke ni ne own infinite amounts thereof. Ni send gxi down preciz mezur
  15,22,Ni send vent pollinators kauxz akv ven cxiel vi trink! Otherwise vi ne keep gxi palatable
  15,23,est ni control life death ni est ultimate inheritors
  15,24,Ni fully kon those vi advance ni fully kon those regress
  15,25,Your Lord surely summon them. Li est Sagx Omniscient